caller_intent: The caller seeks a new garage liability insurance quote for their auto dealership business, 'Always Auto Group LLC,' while providing details about their current policy and business operations.
resolution_steps: Agent requested business details (name, address, phone, email).
Collected business information (operational start date, dealership type, vehicle count, coverage needs).
Noted current policy details (comprehensive/collision coverage, $60k limit).
Initiated new account setup in the system.
Requested current policy documents via email for comparison.
summary: Agent assisted a North Carolina auto dealership owner in initiating a new garage liability insurance quote. The caller provided detailed business information, including operational specifics and current coverage details. The agent began setting up a new account and requested the current policy documents via email for evaluation. Technical system issues were briefly mentioned but did not impede the initial information gathering.
